headline: Dutch-Bangla Bank Achieved The PCI DSS Certification for the Second Time
description: Dutch-Bangla Bank has opened it’s 199th Branch at Ibrahimpur, Kafrul,Dhaka on November 08, 2020. A Dua Mahfil was held seeking blessings of the Almighty Allah for the successful operation of the branch, prosperity of the business community, depositors and stakeholders of the bank. Like the other DBBL Branches, this branch will provide truly On-line Banking facilities including ATM services to the clients from the opening day.
